The site started selling Amazon and NewEgg gift cards in exchange for Bitcoins on June 8, 2011

The price offered on BTC Buy reflects ~10% surcharge. However, the site offers fast turnaround, with most orders filled within less than an hour, which makes it attractive to those who want to spend BTC without wait

